description: For sale: $874,900. Stunning Executive home on over 15 acres with over 500' of lake shore!! Home is nestled on a private road to Nash Lake.This beautiful home offers a light and bright open concept w/ views in every direction! Open vaulted ceilings, gas fireplace, beautiful kitchen with granite counter tops, 4-season porch with walk-out to amazing deck, freshly painted and updated. Wall of windows facing the lake and 360 views of nature. Seller built an 80' x 40' pole barn to store your recreational vehicles. 365 days of recreation; snowmobiling, ice fishing, fishing, boating, & hiking!! Only 35 minutes to the cities. Lots of access to trails. Abundance of privacy and wildlife. Home features a huge flex/office/bonus room above the ample 3 car garage that is fully finished to become your office/boardroom while working from home!! Incredible 30 x 20 deck faces Nash Lake for incredible views and summer fun! Property comes with a dock. this home could easily support horses with the large pole shed! Must see!

Recently sold: $447,000. This home is sale pending. A very clean non-smoker home located within the Sky Harbor development in Webster, MN, Rice County.  (Minneapolis Metro Area) On taxiway #1, with a 50x72 ft hanger with a 40 ft wide x 14 ft electric lift hanger door. The attached hanger is equipped with heated shop, 14 foot tall x 40 foot wide airplane hanger door, 13 ft x 10 ft RV door controlled via new cell phone door opener, and an 18 ft car double garage door. Additional storage above heated shop. Full length workbench along hanger. New finished, insulated, and heated breezeway to garage/hanger. House has a large fully automatic emergency back up generator!  Excellent home for operating a business! The large hanger is attached to the home. Home based businesses welcomed at Sky Harbor! Cabinet shop, Machine Shop, Car restoration, Truckers, Power Sports, Motorcycles...etc. why or lease a business building when you can save $$$ by moving your business to this location. The cost savings increases your income and pays for real estate taxes!  The home is maintenance free on over 1.3 acres. Private well and septic. Low property taxes, and easy south metro commute. If you happen to be a pilot, there is a 2800 ft lighted year round turf runway. Heating is forced air, in floor, and baseboard zoned. Forced air has electrostatic and UV air filtration system. Solar gain from sunny addition family room. Excellent gas fireplace in living room. New roof! Great landscaping with perennial gardens, fruit trees, and nice garden area. Concrete aprons on driveway and hanger ramp leading to taxiway.  Cathedral ceilings and open feeling. A quiet neighborhood. Reverse osmosis drinking water system that also is connected to ice maker for clear and great tasting water. Comfortable whirlpool bath off master, walk in closet.
